<br>
the fact that rogues will have to now choose which buffs they want, and maybe even choose what order they want the buffs in, will mess with rogues, but won't change anything about the way i need HP and STA buffs at a raid.<br>
<br>
at worst, this makes me have to take a moment to click off 5-6 extra unneeded buffs in an xp group that i wouldn't have had to do before, because they were all-in-one. <p>--------------<Br>
